{"tid":969834,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK感情其實好好","createTime":"2019-01-05T10:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T13:08:20.000Z","uid":74065,"like":33,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"68d73e431bcd6efc9c8c9bd19cf6053e69888ad5","tid":969834,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"JENNIE台上「SOLO」！BLACKPINK 3成員一個小動作應援超暖<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3813/d3813200.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3813%2Fd3813200.gif&h=0b82ba93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲JENNIE台上表演，BLACKPINK 3成員都為她應援。（圖／翻攝自JTBC）<br />\n<br />\nJENNIE的個人舞台，先表演一段獨舞，接著演唱個人歌曲《SOLO》，在唱到副歌「閃耀的我的SOLO」，有著招牌的轉手指手勢，鏡頭拍到3位BLACKPINK成員坐在歌手席，都舉起手來跳著轉手指的舞蹈，幫隊友應援，尤其Jisoo還舉得特別高，在JENNIE爆出戀愛緋聞後，成員的互動也讓粉絲感到非常溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJISOO好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dca1e9cdff1f1ee2a6b7aefe2ddef08f983260d","tid":969834,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09223fedbf32e57fddf806836c19cb379c0dbbc2","tid":969834,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dcfbca2c8ac9b8df62d342c4fcde36c80a317e5","tid":969834,"uid":223790,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:56:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1291e7082a095f5308babeb84c07c5704ca6f4c9","tid":969834,"uid":74065,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fXOEw3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfXOEw3U.jpg&h=4fb562d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f3c687ac56755f1abecf9c6daac3d69cf61fc8c","tid":969834,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":0,